prodNameC: 羅氏免疫分析游離三碘甲狀腺素檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent:
M	Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 12mL:
	Streptavidin-coated microparticles, 0.72 mg/mL; binding capacity:
	470 ng biotin/mg microparticles; preservative.
R1	Anti-T3-Ab~Ru(bpy)2+3 (gray cap), 1 bottle, 18mL:
	Monoclonal anti-T3-antibody (sheep) labeled with ruthenium complex
	10 ng/mL; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, pH 7.0; preservative.
R2	T3~biotin (black cap), 1 bottle, 18 mL:
	Biotinylated T3 2 ng/mL; phosphate buffer 100 mmol/L, 
	PH 7.0; preservative.
CalSet:
l	FT3 Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
l	FT3 Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
FT3 in two concentration ranges (approx. 2 pmol/L or 1.3 pg/mL and approx. 40 pmol/L or 26 pg/mL) in a human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民權東路3段2號10樓
efficacy: 定量人類血清和血漿中游離三碘甲狀腺素。
